WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.874 align:middle line:90%


00:00:08.874 --> 00:00:12.325 align:middle line:90%
[THEME MUSIC]

00:00:12.325 --> 00:00:15.283 align:middle line:90%


00:00:15.283 --> 00:00:18.540 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA MEREDITH: We're going
to start this story in 1945

00:00:18.540 --> 00:00:21.120 align:middle line:10%
with the discovery of
the Nag Hammadi texts.

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:24.450 align:middle line:84%
Two Egyptian peasant brothers
found the texts outside a cave

00:00:24.450 --> 00:00:26.970 align:middle line:84%
and brought them home, where
mom burned some of them

00:00:26.970 --> 00:00:28.740 align:middle line:90%
to heat the hut they lived in.

00:00:28.740 --> 00:00:30.540 align:middle line:84%
Peter Canova is
here with us today

00:00:30.540 --> 00:00:33.780 align:middle line:84%
to talk about the ramifications
of millennia of wisdom going

00:00:33.780 --> 00:00:36.030 align:middle line:90%
up in smoke and so much more.

00:00:36.030 --> 00:00:36.927 align:middle line:90%
Welcome, Peter.

00:00:36.927 --> 00:00:38.260 align:middle line:90%
>>PETER CANOVA: Nice to be here.

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:40.302 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: First of all,
what was the significance

00:00:40.302 --> 00:00:41.130 align:middle line:90%
of these scrolls?

00:00:41.130 --> 00:00:44.640 align:middle line:84%
And I love the story that
you relay about the mother

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:47.550 align:middle line:84%
and what happened with
these scrolls and why.

00:00:47.550 --> 00:00:49.592 align:middle line:84%
These things have happened
throughout history.

00:00:49.592 --> 00:00:50.925 align:middle line:90%
And you're thinking, oh, my god.

00:00:50.925 --> 00:00:51.725 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:00:51.725 --> 00:00:55.243 align:middle line:84%
It had a lot of Indiana
Jones-type elements to it.

00:00:55.243 --> 00:00:56.910 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Tell us a
little bit about it.

00:00:56.910 --> 00:00:59.368 align:middle line:84%
Because people don't know that
part of the story, normally.

00:00:59.368 --> 00:01:02.250 align:middle line:10%
>>CANOVA: Well, in 1945,
some Egyptian brothers

00:01:02.250 --> 00:01:06.540 align:middle line:10%
were poking around caves
in the lower mountains

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:08.850 align:middle line:10%
outside of a town called
Nag Hammadi in Egypt.

00:01:08.850 --> 00:01:10.680 align:middle line:90%
And they went into the caves.

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.660 align:middle line:84%
And there were some
earthenware jars in there.

00:01:12.660 --> 00:01:14.860 align:middle line:84%
And they debated whether
to break them open,

00:01:14.860 --> 00:01:16.360 align:middle line:84%
because they were
afraid there might

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:18.340 align:middle line:90%
be an evil jinn in there--

00:01:18.340 --> 00:01:19.570 align:middle line:90%
genie, as they call it.

00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:22.660 align:middle line:90%
A jinn in Islamic terms.

00:01:22.660 --> 00:01:26.080 align:middle line:84%
But their greed overcame their
fear because they said, well,

00:01:26.080 --> 00:01:27.860 align:middle line:90%
then again, it could be gold.

00:01:27.860 --> 00:01:29.500 align:middle line:90%
So they broke it open.

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:33.250 align:middle line:10%
And all these papyrus
scrolls fall out.

00:01:33.250 --> 00:01:36.700 align:middle line:84%
And at first, they said, well,
this has to do with Christians.

00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:38.080 align:middle line:90%
This has nothing to do with us.

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:39.430 align:middle line:90%
Let's just leave it alone.

00:01:39.430 --> 00:01:41.743 align:middle line:84%
But then they said,
well, we don't know.

00:01:41.743 --> 00:01:43.160 align:middle line:84%
Maybe it might be
worth something.

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:44.390 align:middle line:90%
So they took them back home.

00:01:44.390 --> 00:01:48.790 align:middle line:84%
And yes, as you said, mom, not
realizing the value of these,

00:01:48.790 --> 00:01:50.360 align:middle line:90%
used some of them for burning--

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:51.160 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: For fuel.

00:01:51.160 --> 00:01:53.510 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: --the furnace for fuel
for cooking and so forth and so

00:01:53.510 --> 00:01:54.310 align:middle line:90%
on.

00:01:54.310 --> 00:01:56.900 align:middle line:84%
So unfortunately, we lost
some great text there.

00:01:56.900 --> 00:01:58.780 align:middle line:84%
But I think the
significance of it

00:01:58.780 --> 00:02:04.060 align:middle line:84%
is that these texts gave us
the insight, a window, back

00:02:04.060 --> 00:02:06.310 align:middle line:90%
into the old Gnostic masters.

00:02:06.310 --> 00:02:10.060 align:middle line:84%
Now, the Gnostics, that
comes from a Greek word

00:02:10.060 --> 00:02:12.010 align:middle line:90%
"gnosis," which means "to know."

00:02:12.010 --> 00:02:14.890 align:middle line:84%
And the Gnostics were a
group of mystics that were

00:02:14.890 --> 00:02:16.750 align:middle line:90%
centered in Alexandria, Egypt.

00:02:16.750 --> 00:02:21.310 align:middle line:84%
And they were really, I
guess I could say, probably,

00:02:21.310 --> 00:02:23.995 align:middle line:84%
the most scientific
seers of their day,

00:02:23.995 --> 00:02:26.270 align:middle line:84%
as I think we'll get into
a little bit later on.

00:02:26.270 --> 00:02:30.310 align:middle line:84%
But prior to this
time, we had no voice

00:02:30.310 --> 00:02:33.010 align:middle line:84%
of the Gnostic masters, except
through their enemies, which

00:02:33.010 --> 00:02:34.390 align:middle line:90%
were the early church fathers.

00:02:34.390 --> 00:02:37.870 align:middle line:84%
So we really only knew very
much about the Gnostics

00:02:37.870 --> 00:02:40.330 align:middle line:84%
through the writings
of the church fathers.

00:02:40.330 --> 00:02:44.060 align:middle line:84%
And, of course, those were,
rather, hostile point of view.

00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:46.510 align:middle line:84%
But now we were able
to hear directly

00:02:46.510 --> 00:02:48.430 align:middle line:90%
from these old Gnostic masters.

00:02:48.430 --> 00:02:51.730 align:middle line:84%
And it opened up a
whole new perspective

00:02:51.730 --> 00:02:55.540 align:middle line:84%
on early Christianity
and the nature

00:02:55.540 --> 00:02:57.130 align:middle line:84%
of the mystical
Christian church,

00:02:57.130 --> 00:02:59.410 align:middle line:84%
the mystical foundations
of the Christian church.

00:02:59.410 --> 00:03:02.980 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So is it
accurate that it's

00:03:02.980 --> 00:03:04.750 align:middle line:84%
believed that these
texts were written

00:03:04.750 --> 00:03:06.550 align:middle line:84%
around the fourth
and fifth century

00:03:06.550 --> 00:03:11.160 align:middle line:84%
by a sect of Christian monks
who were of a mystical nature?

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:13.180 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Probably
not Christian monks.

00:03:13.180 --> 00:03:14.930 align:middle line:84%
It was probably hidden
by Christian monks.

00:03:14.930 --> 00:03:16.430 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Hidden
by Christian monks.

00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:19.220 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: But the
writings of the Gnostics,

00:03:19.220 --> 00:03:20.700 align:middle line:90%
they vary over time.

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:23.390 align:middle line:84%
Part of the knock that the
Christian church has leveled

00:03:23.390 --> 00:03:25.490 align:middle line:84%
against the Gnostics
is, well, their texts

00:03:25.490 --> 00:03:27.860 align:middle line:84%
came after the writings
of Paul and so forth.

00:03:27.860 --> 00:03:31.460 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's not really true
because the Gospel of Thomas,

00:03:31.460 --> 00:03:34.730 align:middle line:84%
which is clearly Gnostic,
seemed to be dated just

00:03:34.730 --> 00:03:37.670 align:middle line:84%
about the time of the
writings of Paul, about 50

00:03:37.670 --> 00:03:43.670 align:middle line:84%
AD, and yes, the other writings,
although the ones that we have

00:03:43.670 --> 00:03:47.450 align:middle line:84%
appear to have been written
around 100 AD or there.

00:03:47.450 --> 00:03:50.750 align:middle line:84%
We don't know if those were
copies of earlier texts.

00:03:50.750 --> 00:03:54.020 align:middle line:84%
So in other words, there may be
earlier Gnostic texts out there

00:03:54.020 --> 00:03:56.960 align:middle line:84%
that were originals
that we're not aware of,

00:03:56.960 --> 00:03:58.610 align:middle line:90%
and we just got copies.

00:03:58.610 --> 00:04:02.990 align:middle line:84%
But yeah, primarily in the
first century after Christ.

00:04:02.990 --> 00:04:04.850 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So it
would seem, then,

00:04:04.850 --> 00:04:08.030 align:middle line:84%
that because they were talking
about the foundational level

00:04:08.030 --> 00:04:12.090 align:middle line:84%
of the nature of reality, that
this must have been inherited

00:04:12.090 --> 00:04:15.210 align:middle line:84%
and passed-down knowledge
from even Atlantean

00:04:15.210 --> 00:04:17.250 align:middle line:90%
or ancient Egyptian times.

00:04:17.250 --> 00:04:19.729 align:middle line:84%
What is your
understanding of that?

00:04:19.729 --> 00:04:21.600 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Well,
the Gnostics were

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:25.050 align:middle line:84%
very unique because Alexandria
was the intellectual capital

00:04:25.050 --> 00:04:27.660 align:middle line:84%
of the world at that time,
far more so than Rome

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:29.070 align:middle line:90%
or even Athens.

00:04:29.070 --> 00:04:34.240 align:middle line:84%
And you had the confluences
of so many ancient traditions.

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.730 align:middle line:84%
The Hindus, Persian
Zoroastrians,

00:04:37.730 --> 00:04:40.830 align:middle line:84%
the Jewish Kabbalah, Egyptian
Hermeticists, and even

00:04:40.830 --> 00:04:44.070 align:middle line:84%
Hellenistic Greek
philosophy was all part

00:04:44.070 --> 00:04:48.030 align:middle line:84%
of the intellectual mainstream
of Alexandria at that time.

00:04:48.030 --> 00:04:51.780 align:middle line:84%
And the Gnostics really were
the people who synthesized those

00:04:51.780 --> 00:04:55.650 align:middle line:90%
into a coherent understanding.

00:04:55.650 --> 00:04:59.980 align:middle line:84%
But I would also say this
to be really accurate--

00:04:59.980 --> 00:05:03.460 align:middle line:84%
there was a universal spiritual
tradition in ancient times.

00:05:03.460 --> 00:05:05.670 align:middle line:84%
We call it the Perennial
Philosophy today.

00:05:05.670 --> 00:05:10.470 align:middle line:84%
And it had common
elements to it in, really,

00:05:10.470 --> 00:05:11.820 align:middle line:90%
throughout the ancient world.

00:05:11.820 --> 00:05:13.433 align:middle line:84%
Of course, over
the centuries, it

00:05:13.433 --> 00:05:15.600 align:middle line:84%
would have been differentiated
in different cultures

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:16.590 align:middle line:90%
and things like that.

00:05:16.590 --> 00:05:20.280 align:middle line:84%
But it talked about everything
stemming-- all appearances

00:05:20.280 --> 00:05:22.080 align:middle line:90%
stemming from one source.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:24.900 align:middle line:84%
And it described
the nature of light

00:05:24.900 --> 00:05:26.420 align:middle line:84%
and how light
operates and so forth.

00:05:26.420 --> 00:05:28.920 align:middle line:84%
And there were actually what
they called the mystery schools

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:29.833 align:middle line:90%
back in those days.

00:05:29.833 --> 00:05:31.500 align:middle line:84%
And you can think of
the mystery schools

00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:36.900 align:middle line:84%
as an Ivy League of mystical
traditional schools that

00:05:36.900 --> 00:05:38.760 align:middle line:84%
stretched all the
way from India, even

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:40.080 align:middle line:90%
to the British Isles.

00:05:40.080 --> 00:05:42.640 align:middle line:84%
And they all would have
had variances, as I said,

00:05:42.640 --> 00:05:43.440 align:middle line:90%
in their teachings.

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:46.980 align:middle line:84%
But they trained adepts
in the mystical arts

00:05:46.980 --> 00:05:51.480 align:middle line:84%
and in the methodology
of contacting

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:53.610 align:middle line:84%
higher spirit, higher
consciousness, higher

00:05:53.610 --> 00:05:55.000 align:middle line:90%
sources of information.

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:58.620 align:middle line:84%
So that was the foundation
that the Gnostics built on.

00:05:58.620 --> 00:06:00.435 align:middle line:84%
They didn't just
invent all of it.

00:06:00.435 --> 00:06:01.660 align:middle line:90%
They inherited much of it.

00:06:01.660 --> 00:06:06.160 align:middle line:84%
But they collated it and put
it into a very coherent system

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:06.960 align:middle line:90%
of understanding.

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:08.460 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's
what it would seem.

00:06:08.460 --> 00:06:10.410 align:middle line:84%
And talk about up in
smoke, Alexandria.

00:06:10.410 --> 00:06:14.200 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Yeah, unfortunately,
twice actually, the library

00:06:14.200 --> 00:06:15.000 align:middle line:90%
burned.

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:18.450 align:middle line:84%
And then the serapeum, which
was a smaller library, burnt.

00:06:18.450 --> 00:06:21.990 align:middle line:84%
And the knowledge that we
lost is just unfathomable.

00:06:21.990 --> 00:06:25.110 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: By design, I
assume, do you think?

00:06:25.110 --> 00:06:26.740 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: It's hard to say.

00:06:26.740 --> 00:06:28.198 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I mean,
it's speculation.

00:06:28.198 --> 00:06:29.890 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Yeah,
it's hard to say.

00:06:29.890 --> 00:06:31.980 align:middle line:90%
I mean, you can--

00:06:31.980 --> 00:06:34.230 align:middle line:84%
I do think that there's a
principle of opposition that

00:06:34.230 --> 00:06:35.040 align:middle line:90%
exists in this world.

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:35.340 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:06:35.340 --> 00:06:37.632 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: And that great
light attracts great darkness.

00:06:37.632 --> 00:06:40.650 align:middle line:84%
And that, perhaps, circumstances
like that are manifestations.

00:06:40.650 --> 00:06:41.670 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:06:41.670 --> 00:06:43.230 align:middle line:90%
Anyway, so gone.

00:06:43.230 --> 00:06:44.520 align:middle line:90%
So here we are now.

00:06:44.520 --> 00:06:46.590 align:middle line:84%
It takes a couple
thousand years.

00:06:46.590 --> 00:06:48.030 align:middle line:84%
It'll all come
back around people.

00:06:48.030 --> 00:06:50.290 align:middle line:84%
So a lot of the same players
are back around again.

00:06:50.290 --> 00:06:52.920 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about
the creation story.

00:06:52.920 --> 00:06:55.770 align:middle line:84%
And let's go into it as
told in the "Pistis Sophia"

00:06:55.770 --> 00:06:59.310 align:middle line:84%
and why is this
particular body of work

00:06:59.310 --> 00:07:00.960 align:middle line:90%
so important in your mind.

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:05.790 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Well, first
of all, it lays out

00:07:05.790 --> 00:07:09.510 align:middle line:84%
what I believe was the
foundation of quantum physics

00:07:09.510 --> 00:07:12.340 align:middle line:84%
3,000 years before
quantum physics.

00:07:12.340 --> 00:07:19.390 align:middle line:84%
It's so rich in symbolism
and so important

00:07:19.390 --> 00:07:22.570 align:middle line:84%
for understanding the
nature of this world,

00:07:22.570 --> 00:07:29.050 align:middle line:84%
the origin of human beings,
and how reality operates.

00:07:29.050 --> 00:07:30.770 align:middle line:90%
It encompasses all those things.

00:07:30.770 --> 00:07:31.960 align:middle line:90%
So it's very deep.

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:34.060 align:middle line:84%
And I need to take a
little bit of time.

00:07:34.060 --> 00:07:34.330 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah.

00:07:34.330 --> 00:07:35.497 align:middle line:90%
Well, I'm going to ask you--

00:07:35.497 --> 00:07:38.020 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to prompt you
through because it is so rich.

00:07:38.020 --> 00:07:39.130 align:middle line:90%
There's so much to it.

00:07:39.130 --> 00:07:41.350 align:middle line:84%
So I thought-- I just
took it in the flow

00:07:41.350 --> 00:07:42.520 align:middle line:90%
that I found interesting.

00:07:42.520 --> 00:07:42.910 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Sure.

00:07:42.910 --> 00:07:44.493 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And so
we'll go on a journey

00:07:44.493 --> 00:07:46.300 align:middle line:84%
together and interject
anything you want.

00:07:46.300 --> 00:07:46.510 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Sure.

00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:48.280 align:middle line:84%
What I would tell our
listening audience

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:50.650 align:middle line:84%
is, close your eyes
while I'm telling this.

00:07:50.650 --> 00:07:52.690 align:middle line:84%
Because it will
help you visualize

00:07:52.690 --> 00:07:55.495 align:middle line:84%
things that are a little
abstract and sometimes

00:07:55.495 --> 00:07:56.780 align:middle line:90%
hard to grasp.

00:07:56.780 --> 00:08:04.800 align:middle line:84%
So if you just picture a field
of energy that extends out

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:08.520 align:middle line:84%
into infinity, and picture
it as a whitish bubble

00:08:08.520 --> 00:08:12.690 align:middle line:84%
or something with color in
it that extends over a field,

00:08:12.690 --> 00:08:17.800 align:middle line:84%
it radiates out, this energy
was the mind of the source.

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:21.990 align:middle line:84%
This was the source
projecting its energy outward.

00:08:21.990 --> 00:08:24.660 align:middle line:84%
And within this
vast energy field,

00:08:24.660 --> 00:08:27.000 align:middle line:84%
there are pockets
or compartments.

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:29.310 align:middle line:84%
And those pockets
or compartments

00:08:29.310 --> 00:08:32.820 align:middle line:84%
are distinct realities,
localized realities

00:08:32.820 --> 00:08:35.789 align:middle line:84%
of which ours, physical
reality, is one of them.

00:08:35.789 --> 00:08:41.490 align:middle line:84%
And the Sophia story basically
starts off by the one source

00:08:41.490 --> 00:08:48.060 align:middle line:84%
projecting its thought out to
form other spiritual entities

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:49.514 align:middle line:90%
or spiritual beings.

00:08:49.514 --> 00:08:53.400 align:middle line:84%
Now, you can say,
well, it might be

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:58.080 align:middle line:84%
similar to angels in Christian
terminology, but not exactly.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:03.040 align:middle line:84%
What these beings were
were archetypal energies

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:04.630 align:middle line:90%
of the one source itself.

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:06.280 align:middle line:90%
They represented aspects.

00:09:06.280 --> 00:09:08.290 align:middle line:84%
And incidentally, I
call it the source.

00:09:08.290 --> 00:09:09.313 align:middle line:90%
But you can call it God.

00:09:09.313 --> 00:09:10.480 align:middle line:90%
You can call it the source--

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:10.930 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: The creator.

00:09:10.930 --> 00:09:11.410 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: --the creator.

00:09:11.410 --> 00:09:12.827 align:middle line:84%
You can call it
anything you want.

00:09:12.827 --> 00:09:13.850 align:middle line:90%
It's all the same thing.

00:09:13.850 --> 00:09:15.142 align:middle line:90%
The terminology doesn't matter.

00:09:15.142 --> 00:09:18.910 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The point is there
was some presence with minds

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:21.050 align:middle line:84%
so vast it had the
potential to create.

00:09:21.050 --> 00:09:21.850 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Exactly.

00:09:21.850 --> 00:09:24.445 align:middle line:84%
And it had the desire
to expand itself

00:09:24.445 --> 00:09:26.320 align:middle line:84%
throughout different
experiences of creation.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:29.140 align:middle line:84%
And that was the whole
purpose of it generating

00:09:29.140 --> 00:09:30.970 align:middle line:90%
other points of consciousness.

00:09:30.970 --> 00:09:32.980 align:middle line:84%
Because think about
it for a second.

00:09:32.980 --> 00:09:36.565 align:middle line:84%
If you're everything, it's
a rather static existence.

00:09:36.565 --> 00:09:37.900 align:middle line:90%
You can exist.

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:39.760 align:middle line:90%
But you can't really experience.

00:09:39.760 --> 00:09:44.140 align:middle line:84%
You only experience through
contrasts with other beings,

00:09:44.140 --> 00:09:45.520 align:middle line:90%
with other things.

00:09:45.520 --> 00:09:48.250 align:middle line:84%
That's how you
reflect upon yourself,

00:09:48.250 --> 00:09:49.625 align:middle line:90%
is by the contrast around you.

00:09:49.625 --> 00:09:50.500 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:09:50.500 --> 00:09:53.590 align:middle line:84%
So when you're talking about
these beings, these archetypes

00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:56.122 align:middle line:84%
that were created, the way
you explain it in the book,

00:09:56.122 --> 00:09:57.580 align:middle line:84%
it's almost as
though what we would

00:09:57.580 --> 00:10:01.300 align:middle line:84%
call the noble
attributes, you could say,

00:10:01.300 --> 00:10:05.260 align:middle line:84%
of compassion,
beauty, truth, grace.

00:10:05.260 --> 00:10:09.040 align:middle line:84%
These concepts became
archetypal entities.

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:09.880 align:middle line:90%
That's about that.

00:10:09.880 --> 00:10:11.047 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: That's exactly it.

00:10:11.047 --> 00:10:13.810 align:middle line:84%
These spiritual entities,
which were really

00:10:13.810 --> 00:10:16.630 align:middle line:84%
sources of intelligent
energy in and of themselves,

00:10:16.630 --> 00:10:21.610 align:middle line:84%
were aspects of the
deity, aspects of God,

00:10:21.610 --> 00:10:22.820 align:middle line:90%
aspects of the source.

00:10:22.820 --> 00:10:26.700 align:middle line:84%
They were given names like
truth, justice, beauty, wisdom,

00:10:26.700 --> 00:10:28.840 align:middle line:84%
all these beautiful
attributes, which

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:31.390 align:middle line:84%
are archetypal images
that even extend down

00:10:31.390 --> 00:10:33.610 align:middle line:90%
into our level of existence.

00:10:33.610 --> 00:10:36.010 align:middle line:84%
These are archetypes
that have guided humanity

00:10:36.010 --> 00:10:37.015 align:middle line:90%
through art and poetry--

00:10:37.015 --> 00:10:37.330 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The
Noble Truths, yeah.

00:10:37.330 --> 00:10:39.850 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: --and the Noble
Truths throughout the ages.

00:10:39.850 --> 00:10:44.260 align:middle line:84%
So the process by which
these beings were generated

00:10:44.260 --> 00:10:46.990 align:middle line:84%
is important to understand
because it was actually

00:10:46.990 --> 00:10:49.870 align:middle line:90%
a process of limitation.

00:10:49.870 --> 00:10:53.200 align:middle line:84%
When I told you that
the source projected out

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:57.130 align:middle line:84%
this vast field of energy,
which they call the quantum

00:10:57.130 --> 00:11:00.970 align:middle line:84%
fields in modern
terminology, there

00:11:00.970 --> 00:11:04.190 align:middle line:84%
are parallel dimensions
or parallel universes

00:11:04.190 --> 00:11:04.990 align:middle line:90%
within that field.

00:11:04.990 --> 00:11:08.050 align:middle line:84%
As I told you, there's
compartments within that field.

00:11:08.050 --> 00:11:10.600 align:middle line:84%
Now, those compartments
are not really spatial.

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:12.530 align:middle line:84%
People like to think
in terms of space.

00:11:12.530 --> 00:11:15.765 align:middle line:84%
But what they really were were
frequencies of vibrations.

00:11:15.765 --> 00:11:16.890 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Frequencies, yes.

00:11:16.890 --> 00:11:19.490 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Differing frequencies
created different dimensions

00:11:19.490 --> 00:11:20.290 align:middle line:90%
of existence.

00:11:20.290 --> 00:11:21.708 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Like the
multiverse is--

00:11:21.708 --> 00:11:22.750 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: The multiverse.

00:11:22.750 --> 00:11:23.815 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: --the collection
of these frequencies.

00:11:23.815 --> 00:11:24.850 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Exactly.

00:11:24.850 --> 00:11:27.875 align:middle line:84%
And these spiritual beings,
which were called aeons,

00:11:27.875 --> 00:11:31.750 align:middle line:84%
A-E-O-N-S, which means
eternities in Greek,

00:11:31.750 --> 00:11:38.710 align:middle line:84%
and they represented the forces
that helped shape the creation

00:11:38.710 --> 00:11:41.620 align:middle line:84%
in the way that the
creator wanted to do it.

00:11:41.620 --> 00:11:45.460 align:middle line:84%
They were working in harmony or
with the will of the creator.

00:11:45.460 --> 00:11:49.840 align:middle line:84%
But they had a sense
of self-identity.

00:11:49.840 --> 00:11:51.430 align:middle line:84%
They realized they
were themselves.

00:11:51.430 --> 00:11:53.650 align:middle line:84%
But they realized they
were part of the source.

00:11:53.650 --> 00:11:54.550 align:middle line:90%
Now--

00:11:54.550 --> 00:11:56.500 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But let me
just say something.

00:11:56.500 --> 00:11:58.850 align:middle line:84%
At this point, this was
almost pure thought-form--

00:11:58.850 --> 00:11:59.650 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yes.

00:11:59.650 --> 00:12:00.590 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --existence?

00:12:00.590 --> 00:12:01.390 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:12:01.390 --> 00:12:04.095 align:middle line:84%
There was no material
reality at this time.

00:12:04.095 --> 00:12:06.220 align:middle line:84%
And that's where we're
going to go in a little bit.

00:12:06.220 --> 00:12:07.110 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: That's correct.

00:12:07.110 --> 00:12:07.910 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:12:07.910 --> 00:12:10.060 align:middle line:90%
Now, we have these archetypes.

00:12:10.060 --> 00:12:13.420 align:middle line:84%
And as in all things,
learning through contrast,

00:12:13.420 --> 00:12:18.580 align:middle line:84%
then did this creative force
create their mirror reflection

00:12:18.580 --> 00:12:19.840 align:middle line:90%
in the negative?

00:12:19.840 --> 00:12:23.440 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Well, that-- you
have to go a little bit further

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:25.510 align:middle line:84%
into the story to get
to that part of it.

00:12:25.510 --> 00:12:27.545 align:middle line:84%
And we were talking
about Sophia.

00:12:27.545 --> 00:12:28.345 align:middle line:90%
And here--

00:12:28.345 --> 00:12:29.860 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, we're going
to spend a lot of time on her.

00:12:29.860 --> 00:12:30.130 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:12:30.130 --> 00:12:31.990 align:middle line:84%
And here's where Sophia
comes into the story.

00:12:31.990 --> 00:12:33.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I call her God's girl.

00:12:33.040 --> 00:12:33.840 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:37.660 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: The youngest of
these aeons that were created

00:12:37.660 --> 00:12:40.360 align:middle line:84%
was Sophia, whose
name means wisdom.

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:42.492 align:middle line:84%
And incidentally, the
only reason most people

00:12:42.492 --> 00:12:44.200 align:middle line:84%
aren't familiar with
Sophia-- because she

00:12:44.200 --> 00:12:46.540 align:middle line:84%
is a character in the
Bible, particularly

00:12:46.540 --> 00:12:47.560 align:middle line:90%
in the Old Testament.

00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:49.840 align:middle line:90%
But she's called wisdom, and--

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:50.770 align:middle line:90%
instead of Sophia.

00:12:50.770 --> 00:12:52.900 align:middle line:84%
Sophia is the Greek
word for wisdom.

00:12:52.900 --> 00:12:56.020 align:middle line:84%
The English translations that
we got use the term wisdom.

00:12:56.020 --> 00:13:00.490 align:middle line:84%
And she is a very prominent
figure in the Book of Job.

00:13:00.490 --> 00:13:03.550 align:middle line:84%
And in Proverbs, she says, "I
was there from the beginning.

00:13:03.550 --> 00:13:06.880 align:middle line:84%
I was there with the creator
at the beginning," meaning

00:13:06.880 --> 00:13:08.470 align:middle line:90%
she was one of the eternities.

00:13:08.470 --> 00:13:13.480 align:middle line:84%
So each of these
eternities had--

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:15.550 align:middle line:84%
it was a little bit of
a hierarchy in a sense.

00:13:15.550 --> 00:13:17.890 align:middle line:84%
Because we talked
about limitation.

00:13:17.890 --> 00:13:20.560 align:middle line:84%
And the way you
experience individuality

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:22.150 align:middle line:90%
is through limitation.

00:13:22.150 --> 00:13:27.790 align:middle line:84%
What made any of these aeons or
spiritual beings differentiated

00:13:27.790 --> 00:13:31.150 align:middle line:84%
from one another was their
level of spiritual vibration.

00:13:31.150 --> 00:13:34.000 align:middle line:90%
So it worked its way on down.

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:36.745 align:middle line:84%
So the closer you
were to the source,

00:13:36.745 --> 00:13:38.240 align:middle line:90%
the higher the vibration was.

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:39.040 align:middle line:90%
The more--

00:13:39.040 --> 00:13:41.110 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So truth and beauty
were above, it turns out,

00:13:41.110 --> 00:13:41.910 align:middle line:90%
wisdom?

00:13:41.910 --> 00:13:42.920 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yes.

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:45.790 align:middle line:84%
And when you worked
your way down,

00:13:45.790 --> 00:13:47.770 align:middle line:84%
there was a little
bit of dilution.

00:13:47.770 --> 00:13:52.570 align:middle line:84%
Now, still very high spiritual
being, very godlike high

00:13:52.570 --> 00:13:57.220 align:middle line:84%
spiritual beings, but there
was a differentiation in terms

00:13:57.220 --> 00:13:59.650 align:middle line:90%
of the spiritual vibration.

00:13:59.650 --> 00:14:02.480 align:middle line:84%
What I liken it to
is you have a CD.

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:05.060 align:middle line:84%
And then you make a copy of
that CD and a copy of that copy

00:14:05.060 --> 00:14:06.140 align:middle line:90%
and a copy of that copy.

00:14:06.140 --> 00:14:08.930 align:middle line:84%
Well, the original has the
greatest clarity and fidelity.

00:14:08.930 --> 00:14:11.180 align:middle line:84%
The subsequent copies are
all a little bit diluted.

00:14:11.180 --> 00:14:12.620 align:middle line:84%
They're very close,
very similar,

00:14:12.620 --> 00:14:14.150 align:middle line:84%
but they're a
little bit diluted.

00:14:14.150 --> 00:14:18.680 align:middle line:84%
So Sophia was the last of these
aeons or these spiritual beings

00:14:18.680 --> 00:14:20.000 align:middle line:90%
to be created.

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:21.920 align:middle line:90%
And she was wisdom.

00:14:21.920 --> 00:14:23.840 align:middle line:90%
So how does wisdom grow?

00:14:23.840 --> 00:14:26.130 align:middle line:84%
Well, it only grows
through experience.

00:14:26.130 --> 00:14:30.140 align:middle line:84%
So Sophia had this desire
to create on her own,

00:14:30.140 --> 00:14:32.540 align:middle line:84%
to create the way
the creator did.

00:14:32.540 --> 00:14:35.180 align:middle line:84%
Because none of the
aeons really understood

00:14:35.180 --> 00:14:36.890 align:middle line:84%
the deeper mysteries
of the creator.

00:14:36.890 --> 00:14:39.710 align:middle line:84%
And she longed to know
these deeper mysteries.

00:14:39.710 --> 00:14:45.410 align:middle line:84%
So Sophia looks outside of this
original sphere of creation,

00:14:45.410 --> 00:14:49.460 align:middle line:84%
which would be the source and
these aeons or these entities.

00:14:49.460 --> 00:14:53.090 align:middle line:84%
She looks outside of
that sphere of creation.

00:14:53.090 --> 00:14:57.670 align:middle line:84%
And she looks into something
called chaos, again,

00:14:57.670 --> 00:14:58.750 align:middle line:90%
another quantum term.

00:14:58.750 --> 00:15:01.240 align:middle line:84%
We have chaos theory
in quantum physics.

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:03.760 align:middle line:84%
But what chaos
really represented

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:07.187 align:middle line:84%
was the unorganized part
of this spiritual field

00:15:07.187 --> 00:15:09.145 align:middle line:84%
that had not been organized
by the mind of God.

00:15:09.145 --> 00:15:11.965 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And in Hermetics, it
would be called prima materia?

00:15:11.965 --> 00:15:13.150 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Right.

00:15:13.150 --> 00:15:14.080 align:middle line:84%
That would be
another name for it.

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:15.410 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Another name for it.

00:15:15.410 --> 00:15:19.180 align:middle line:84%
And if you go to the
Egyptian lexicon,

00:15:19.180 --> 00:15:21.100 align:middle line:84%
you could almost
say what she was

00:15:21.100 --> 00:15:23.267 align:middle line:84%
doing was a function of
what would be known as ISIS.

00:15:23.267 --> 00:15:24.067 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Mm-hmm.

00:15:24.067 --> 00:15:25.880 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So let's
talk about that now.

00:15:25.880 --> 00:15:27.050 align:middle line:90%
So this is really important.

00:15:27.050 --> 00:15:31.615 align:middle line:84%
She wants to have experience to
be able to expand her wisdom.

00:15:31.615 --> 00:15:35.440 align:middle line:84%
She is now reaching into
the already existing field

00:15:35.440 --> 00:15:38.860 align:middle line:84%
of chaos, prima materia,
quantum soup, whatever, chaos.

00:15:38.860 --> 00:15:41.930 align:middle line:84%
She's reaching into it to
put an imprint upon it,

00:15:41.930 --> 00:15:43.745 align:middle line:90%
which is creation, just like--

00:15:43.745 --> 00:15:44.545 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:15:44.545 --> 00:15:45.345 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yes.

00:15:45.345 --> 00:15:48.860 align:middle line:84%
And what happens is
something very interesting.

00:15:48.860 --> 00:15:54.220 align:middle line:84%
She projects her high energy,
her divine essence into chaos.

00:15:54.220 --> 00:15:57.970 align:middle line:84%
And something very
weird happens there.

00:15:57.970 --> 00:16:01.078 align:middle line:90%
Chaos is not an empty vacuum.

00:16:01.078 --> 00:16:03.370 align:middle line:84%
And science has found--
quantum physics has found there

00:16:03.370 --> 00:16:04.780 align:middle line:90%
is no such thing as a vacuum.

00:16:04.780 --> 00:16:07.570 align:middle line:84%
In space, all around us,
it's seething with virtual

00:16:07.570 --> 00:16:09.860 align:middle line:84%
particles, particles
that have-- in potential,

00:16:09.860 --> 00:16:10.660 align:middle line:90%
that have not yet--

00:16:10.660 --> 00:16:11.650 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Waiting
to be imprinted.

00:16:11.650 --> 00:16:13.358 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: --that have
not yet come into--

00:16:13.358 --> 00:16:15.580 align:middle line:84%
manifested into what
we would call reality.

00:16:15.580 --> 00:16:19.893 align:middle line:84%
So chaos is seething
with protomatter.

00:16:19.893 --> 00:16:22.060 align:middle line:84%
Now, this blows my mind
that they could even give it

00:16:22.060 --> 00:16:24.370 align:middle line:84%
a term like this--
"protomatter," that

00:16:24.370 --> 00:16:28.330 align:middle line:84%
which becomes before matter,
which is virtual particles.

00:16:28.330 --> 00:16:30.910 align:middle line:84%
Chaos is seething with
these virtual particles.

00:16:30.910 --> 00:16:34.240 align:middle line:84%
And they swarm around
Sofia like iron filings

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:35.630 align:middle line:90%
would swarm to a magnet.

00:16:35.630 --> 00:16:37.190 align:middle line:90%
And they engulf her.

00:16:37.190 --> 00:16:40.990 align:middle line:84%
They start to activate
with her high energy.

00:16:40.990 --> 00:16:43.910 align:middle line:84%
But they're draining
her energy off.

00:16:43.910 --> 00:16:46.940 align:middle line:84%
And something is-- new
is starting to form here.

00:16:46.940 --> 00:16:50.300 align:middle line:84%
She cries out to heaven,
I am becoming as lead.

00:16:50.300 --> 00:16:53.000 align:middle line:84%
Save me from this matter
that I am becoming.

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:54.380 align:middle line:90%
My light is diminishing.

00:16:54.380 --> 00:16:56.570 align:middle line:90%
Save me from this matter.

00:16:56.570 --> 00:17:03.230 align:middle line:84%
What we see here is the whole
functioning of the God particle

00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:04.069 align:middle line:90%
in quantum physics.

00:17:04.069 --> 00:17:05.837 align:middle line:90%
Now, the God particle--

00:17:05.837 --> 00:17:08.420 align:middle line:84%
there's something that surrounds
our universe called the Higgs

00:17:08.420 --> 00:17:10.849 align:middle line:84%
field, all
encompassing-- and there

00:17:10.849 --> 00:17:12.530 align:middle line:84%
are virtual particles
in the Higgs field

00:17:12.530 --> 00:17:13.730 align:middle line:90%
they call Higgs bosons.

00:17:13.730 --> 00:17:16.910 align:middle line:84%
Now, they discovered
the Higgs bosons in 2012

00:17:16.910 --> 00:17:19.940 align:middle line:84%
in the giant particle
collider in Switzerland,

00:17:19.940 --> 00:17:22.069 align:middle line:84%
underneath Switzerland
and France.

00:17:22.069 --> 00:17:25.167 align:middle line:84%
And they-- it was theorized
for like 50 years.

00:17:25.167 --> 00:17:27.000 align:middle line:84%
But they finally found
out it was a reality.

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:29.720 align:middle line:84%
And what the Higgs
bosons do is that when

00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:32.810 align:middle line:84%
energy enters into our
universe-- and incidentally,

00:17:32.810 --> 00:17:34.700 align:middle line:84%
science has no idea
what energy is.

00:17:34.700 --> 00:17:36.200 align:middle line:84%
They don't know
where it comes from.

00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:38.090 align:middle line:84%
They can manipulate it
to a certain extent.

00:17:38.090 --> 00:17:39.680 align:middle line:90%
But they don't know its origins.

00:17:39.680 --> 00:17:42.110 align:middle line:84%
And they don't really
understand what energy is.

00:17:42.110 --> 00:17:45.255 align:middle line:84%
So energy comes into our
universe from somewhere.

00:17:45.255 --> 00:17:46.055 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:17:46.055 --> 00:17:49.340 align:middle line:10%
>>CANOVA: And the Higgs
bosons attach themselves

00:17:49.340 --> 00:17:52.400 align:middle line:10%
to these high streams of
energy and slow them down.

00:17:52.400 --> 00:17:54.650 align:middle line:10%
And they slow them
to the point where

00:17:54.650 --> 00:17:57.660 align:middle line:10%
they start to take on mass,
because that's what matter is.

00:17:57.660 --> 00:18:01.360 align:middle line:84%
Matter is simply energy in
a lower state of vibration.

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:04.140 align:middle line:84%
So they lower the vibration
of this high energy.

00:18:04.140 --> 00:18:08.640 align:middle line:84%
And it starts to
form mass or matter--

00:18:08.640 --> 00:18:10.560 align:middle line:84%
what was happening
in the Sophia story.

00:18:10.560 --> 00:18:11.790 align:middle line:90%
They swarmed around Sophia.

00:18:11.790 --> 00:18:13.170 align:middle line:90%
They lowered her high energy.

00:18:13.170 --> 00:18:15.840 align:middle line:84%
And she cries out,
I'm becoming matter.

00:18:15.840 --> 00:18:17.340 align:middle line:90%
So here, you see the function.

00:18:17.340 --> 00:18:20.070 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's so clear that you
see the function of the God

00:18:20.070 --> 00:18:22.800 align:middle line:84%
particle and the energy-matter
conversion happening

00:18:22.800 --> 00:18:24.030 align:middle line:90%
in this story right there.

00:18:24.030 --> 00:18:24.570 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:18:24.570 --> 00:18:25.860 align:middle line:90%
And that does seem very clear.

00:18:25.860 --> 00:18:29.100 align:middle line:84%
There is a point in this story,
though, that is interesting.

00:18:29.100 --> 00:18:34.110 align:middle line:84%
Because, as you say in this,
she was, supposedly, only half

00:18:34.110 --> 00:18:36.300 align:middle line:90%
of the wisdom equation.

00:18:36.300 --> 00:18:38.790 align:middle line:90%
You say she had a counterpart.

00:18:38.790 --> 00:18:39.900 align:middle line:90%
Is that correct?

00:18:39.900 --> 00:18:43.080 align:middle line:84%
Or was she standing
on her own as wisdom?

00:18:43.080 --> 00:18:44.970 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: She acted on her own.

00:18:44.970 --> 00:18:46.610 align:middle line:90%
But she was part of a pairing.

00:18:46.610 --> 00:18:48.360 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, now
let's talk about that.

00:18:48.360 --> 00:18:49.740 align:middle line:84%
And did the others
have pairings?

00:18:49.740 --> 00:18:51.060 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yes, there was--

00:18:51.060 --> 00:18:53.730 align:middle line:84%
OK, this really gets back into
something very fundamental

00:18:53.730 --> 00:18:56.440 align:middle line:84%
in understanding the
whole process of creation,

00:18:56.440 --> 00:18:59.790 align:middle line:84%
which is that although
everything stems from one

00:18:59.790 --> 00:19:02.770 align:middle line:84%
source, that one source-- the
characteristics of that one

00:19:02.770 --> 00:19:03.570 align:middle line:90%
source was--

00:19:03.570 --> 00:19:05.460 align:middle line:84%
divided itself into
a polarity that we

00:19:05.460 --> 00:19:07.900 align:middle line:90%
call yin-yang, male and female.

00:19:07.900 --> 00:19:10.530 align:middle line:84%
And it was the interaction
of that polarity,

00:19:10.530 --> 00:19:13.020 align:middle line:84%
that positive and negative,
the interaction between them

00:19:13.020 --> 00:19:17.730 align:middle line:84%
that generated the light, heat,
and energy to fundamentally

00:19:17.730 --> 00:19:18.840 align:middle line:90%
spur on creation.

00:19:18.840 --> 00:19:22.680 align:middle line:84%
So because these spiritual
beings, the aeons,

00:19:22.680 --> 00:19:24.840 align:middle line:84%
were made in the
image of their father,

00:19:24.840 --> 00:19:27.360 align:middle line:90%
they too were polarities.

00:19:27.360 --> 00:19:29.940 align:middle line:84%
They had a male and
a female counterpart.

00:19:29.940 --> 00:19:33.910 align:middle line:84%
So Sophia had a
male counterpart.

00:19:33.910 --> 00:19:35.935 align:middle line:84%
It was given different
names in different texts.

00:19:35.935 --> 00:19:37.560 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, I'd
be curious to know.

00:19:37.560 --> 00:19:39.600 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: One of them was
called Thelema or will, OK?

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:40.400 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:19:40.400 --> 00:19:42.570 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: So wisdom and
will were a pairing.

00:19:42.570 --> 00:19:43.620 align:middle line:90%
There were other ones.

00:19:43.620 --> 00:19:45.630 align:middle line:90%
But I won't digress into that.

00:19:45.630 --> 00:19:47.340 align:middle line:90%
But she acted--

00:19:47.340 --> 00:19:49.800 align:middle line:84%
Sophia, the thing
that she did that

00:19:49.800 --> 00:19:53.400 align:middle line:84%
was radical and represented
the first fall of spirit,

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:55.230 align:middle line:90%
the first break from heaven--

00:19:55.230 --> 00:19:58.080 align:middle line:84%
from the heavenly
realm was that she

00:19:58.080 --> 00:20:02.820 align:middle line:84%
created without the consent
of her counterpart--

00:20:02.820 --> 00:20:06.480 align:middle line:84%
her male counterpart and without
the consent of the creator.

00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:08.730 align:middle line:84%
So those were the
two preconditions

00:20:08.730 --> 00:20:11.640 align:middle line:84%
for how creation happened
within the divine realm.

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:15.720 align:middle line:84%
It would be an agreement
between the male and the female

00:20:15.720 --> 00:20:20.100 align:middle line:84%
essentially blessed or
okayed by the "big guy."

00:20:20.100 --> 00:20:22.750 align:middle line:84%
But Sophia didn't
have any of that.

00:20:22.750 --> 00:20:24.510 align:middle line:90%
She acted completely on her own.

00:20:24.510 --> 00:20:27.360 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, many
of the texts say

00:20:27.360 --> 00:20:32.438 align:middle line:84%
that she was very imprudent,
and she committed a great sin.

00:20:32.438 --> 00:20:34.230 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: We're going
to debate that later.

00:20:34.230 --> 00:20:35.010 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: That could be debated.

00:20:35.010 --> 00:20:36.065 align:middle line:90%
That could be debated.

00:20:36.065 --> 00:20:38.190 align:middle line:84%
There's two sides of that
coin that we can look at.

00:20:38.190 --> 00:20:38.990 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:20:38.990 --> 00:20:41.835 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: But getting back
to the Sophia story, so all

00:20:41.835 --> 00:20:45.090 align:middle line:84%
of a sudden, this new dimension
of matter was happening.

00:20:45.090 --> 00:20:47.340 align:middle line:84%
Now, I want to caution you
that this is not matter

00:20:47.340 --> 00:20:48.240 align:middle line:90%
as we know it.

00:20:48.240 --> 00:20:53.143 align:middle line:84%
These were finer, more like
forms of matter, but forms

00:20:53.143 --> 00:20:54.060 align:middle line:90%
of matter nonetheless.

00:20:54.060 --> 00:20:55.710 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It was
a field that could

00:20:55.710 --> 00:20:59.050 align:middle line:84%
be expressed once it had
instruction or imprint or logos

00:20:59.050 --> 00:20:59.850 align:middle line:90%
applied to it.

00:20:59.850 --> 00:21:01.380 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Yeah, and there's
all degrees of matter.

00:21:01.380 --> 00:21:02.190 align:middle line:90%
There's finer degrees.

00:21:02.190 --> 00:21:03.120 align:middle line:90%
And there's denser degrees.

00:21:03.120 --> 00:21:04.080 align:middle line:90%
We would be pretty dense.

00:21:04.080 --> 00:21:05.437 align:middle line:84%
There's finer degrees
of matter that we--

00:21:05.437 --> 00:21:06.729 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And other dimensions.

00:21:06.729 --> 00:21:08.430 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: --wouldn't
be able to detect.

00:21:08.430 --> 00:21:13.080 align:middle line:84%
So this new dimension of
matter could no longer

00:21:13.080 --> 00:21:15.542 align:middle line:84%
coexist with the
spiritual dimension--

00:21:15.542 --> 00:21:17.250 align:middle line:84%
the high-energy, the
spiritual dimension.

00:21:17.250 --> 00:21:18.660 align:middle line:90%
They were two different states.

00:21:18.660 --> 00:21:20.320 align:middle line:90%
They could not coexist.

00:21:20.320 --> 00:21:25.350 align:middle line:84%
So the texts say that this new
dimension was projected apart

00:21:25.350 --> 00:21:29.160 align:middle line:84%
in a violent upheaval
and exploded out

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.250 align:middle line:90%
into another dimension.

00:21:30.250 --> 00:21:31.500 align:middle line:90%
Well, what is that describing?

00:21:31.500 --> 00:21:31.890 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Well--

00:21:31.890 --> 00:21:32.520 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: The Big Bang.

00:21:32.520 --> 00:21:32.850 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:21:32.850 --> 00:21:33.650 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:21:33.650 --> 00:21:37.890 align:middle line:84%
So here, we've already seen
the Gnostic texts describing

00:21:37.890 --> 00:21:40.490 align:middle line:84%
the existence of
parallel dimensions,

00:21:40.490 --> 00:21:43.300 align:middle line:84%
the energy-matter conversion
of the God particle,

00:21:43.300 --> 00:21:46.538 align:middle line:84%
the origin of matter,
and the Big Bang.

00:21:46.538 --> 00:21:48.580 align:middle line:84%
And the Big Bang, essentially,
was the appearance

00:21:48.580 --> 00:21:51.665 align:middle line:84%
of something out of nothing, the
appearance of our universe out

00:21:51.665 --> 00:21:52.540 align:middle line:90%
of seemingly nothing.

00:21:52.540 --> 00:21:55.040 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It doesn't mean it
was literally a solo explosion.

00:21:55.040 --> 00:21:56.572 align:middle line:90%
It just came out of nothing.

00:21:56.572 --> 00:21:58.780 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: It came out of
nothing from our standpoint.

00:21:58.780 --> 00:21:59.050 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's right.

00:21:59.050 --> 00:21:59.605 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: From our standpoint.

00:21:59.605 --> 00:22:00.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: From our standpoint.

00:22:00.040 --> 00:22:00.865 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Because
we're looking at it--

00:22:00.865 --> 00:22:00.910 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:22:00.910 --> 00:22:02.540 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: --from this
side of the equation.

00:22:02.540 --> 00:22:03.730 align:middle line:84%
The other side of
the equation, it

00:22:03.730 --> 00:22:04.150 align:middle line:84%
would be something
quite different.

00:22:04.150 --> 00:22:05.125 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The other
side of the horizon.

00:22:05.125 --> 00:22:06.490 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:22:06.490 --> 00:22:10.300 align:middle line:84%
So right there, you
see descriptions

00:22:10.300 --> 00:22:12.640 align:middle line:84%
of some of the major theories
of modern quantum physics.

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:15.250 align:middle line:84%
And also, I should
mention the quantum field,

00:22:15.250 --> 00:22:16.360 align:middle line:90%
the virtual particles.

00:22:16.360 --> 00:22:19.270 align:middle line:84%
All these things were
described in the Gnostic texts.

00:22:19.270 --> 00:22:22.612 align:middle line:84%
Of course, they didn't always
use the exact same terminology.

00:22:22.612 --> 00:22:24.820 align:middle line:84%
We didn't have particle
colliders back in those days.

00:22:24.820 --> 00:22:28.240 align:middle line:84%
We didn't have the technical
capabilities in those days

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:29.050 align:middle line:90%
to describe them.

00:22:29.050 --> 00:22:30.880 align:middle line:84%
But it's about as
close as you can

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:32.172 align:middle line:90%
get to a description of these--

00:22:32.172 --> 00:22:34.130 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Just because
we didn't have machinery

00:22:34.130 --> 00:22:36.130 align:middle line:84%
to prove it didn't mean
they didn't already

00:22:36.130 --> 00:22:37.210 align:middle line:90%
know and understand it.

00:22:37.210 --> 00:22:38.410 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Or have their
ways to describe it.

00:22:38.410 --> 00:22:39.745 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And have their ways
of describing it, exactly.

00:22:39.745 --> 00:22:40.545 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Exactly.

00:22:40.545 --> 00:22:42.280 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So now
we have creation.

00:22:42.280 --> 00:22:44.350 align:middle line:84%
At this point, is
that where you would

00:22:44.350 --> 00:22:48.220 align:middle line:84%
say some of the mere
reflections of the Noble Truths

00:22:48.220 --> 00:22:51.340 align:middle line:84%
started coming into
play, the game of light

00:22:51.340 --> 00:22:54.700 align:middle line:84%
and dark and polarity in terms
of the creation of entities

00:22:54.700 --> 00:22:58.875 align:middle line:84%
that later became influential
in the cosmos and on our planet?

00:22:58.875 --> 00:23:01.900 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Well, when you
talk about light and dark,

00:23:01.900 --> 00:23:04.300 align:middle line:84%
you have to understand
that opposition

00:23:04.300 --> 00:23:06.100 align:middle line:90%
existed from the beginning.

00:23:06.100 --> 00:23:09.100 align:middle line:84%
And the reason
for opposition was

00:23:09.100 --> 00:23:13.510 align:middle line:84%
that in order for
these created beings

00:23:13.510 --> 00:23:18.310 align:middle line:84%
to be individuals that have free
will, they had to have choice.

00:23:18.310 --> 00:23:21.680 align:middle line:84%
So opposition is what
gave them the choice.

00:23:21.680 --> 00:23:24.850 align:middle line:84%
And the choice was, at least
as far as Sofia is concerned,

00:23:24.850 --> 00:23:29.410 align:middle line:84%
you either subordinate
your will to God's will,

00:23:29.410 --> 00:23:32.560 align:middle line:84%
or you pursue your
own individuality.

00:23:32.560 --> 00:23:37.390 align:middle line:84%
When Sofia fell from heaven,
this was the first fall.

00:23:37.390 --> 00:23:40.440 align:middle line:84%
In the Gnostic tradition,
there's more than one fall.

00:23:40.440 --> 00:23:42.900 align:middle line:84%
The first fall was
Sofia's fall from heaven.

00:23:42.900 --> 00:23:47.657 align:middle line:84%
And what it created was also
the dimension of soul-mind.

00:23:47.657 --> 00:23:49.740 align:middle line:84%
Now, there's a difference
between soul and spirit.

00:23:49.740 --> 00:23:51.255 align:middle line:84%
Most people use those
interchangeably.

00:23:51.255 --> 00:23:51.690 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Let's talk about that.

00:23:51.690 --> 00:23:53.040 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: OK.

00:23:53.040 --> 00:23:56.550 align:middle line:84%
The difference-- spirit is
that consciousness that never

00:23:56.550 --> 00:23:59.170 align:middle line:90%
left the sphere of the source.

00:23:59.170 --> 00:24:01.590 align:middle line:84%
Its will is the
will of the source.

00:24:01.590 --> 00:24:02.910 align:middle line:90%
They are individuals.

00:24:02.910 --> 00:24:05.130 align:middle line:84%
But they recognize
themselves as themselves.

00:24:05.130 --> 00:24:07.080 align:middle line:84%
And they recognize
themselves as the source--

00:24:07.080 --> 00:24:08.670 align:middle line:90%
as part of the source.

00:24:08.670 --> 00:24:11.430 align:middle line:84%
Soul, on the other
hand, is the record

00:24:11.430 --> 00:24:13.495 align:middle line:84%
of spirit pursuing
its own individuality

00:24:13.495 --> 00:24:15.120 align:middle line:84%
through different
realms of experience.

00:24:15.120 --> 00:24:16.770 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's a good
way to describe it.

00:24:16.770 --> 00:24:19.320 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: And, of course, you
accumulate the Akashic record

00:24:19.320 --> 00:24:20.280 align:middle line:90%
and everything else.

00:24:20.280 --> 00:24:22.710 align:middle line:84%
That all has to do with
soul and soul-mind.

00:24:22.710 --> 00:24:29.400 align:middle line:84%
So soul and spirit are
really two different states.

00:24:29.400 --> 00:24:31.740 align:middle line:84%
The dimension that
Sophia created

00:24:31.740 --> 00:24:35.610 align:middle line:84%
would, of course,
involve ego, because she

00:24:35.610 --> 00:24:39.010 align:middle line:84%
was acting on her own for
herself for her own experience.

00:24:39.010 --> 00:24:42.430 align:middle line:84%
So ego was part
of that equation.

00:24:42.430 --> 00:24:48.680 align:middle line:84%
And opposition,
as you go lower--

00:24:48.680 --> 00:24:50.690 align:middle line:84%
into lower and lower
levels of creation,

00:24:50.690 --> 00:24:53.060 align:middle line:84%
can take on the appearance
of what we call evil.

00:24:53.060 --> 00:24:57.950 align:middle line:84%
The opposition in and of itself
in the abstract is not evil.

00:24:57.950 --> 00:25:01.730 align:middle line:84%
In fact, the devil in
early Judaic tradition

00:25:01.730 --> 00:25:04.440 align:middle line:84%
was not the horned being with
cloven hooves and everything

00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:05.240 align:middle line:90%
else.

00:25:05.240 --> 00:25:07.400 align:middle line:84%
He was called the
Angel of Opposition.

00:25:07.400 --> 00:25:11.930 align:middle line:84%
And he was sent by
the creator to create

00:25:11.930 --> 00:25:14.180 align:middle line:84%
obstacles for human
beings to overcome

00:25:14.180 --> 00:25:15.470 align:middle line:90%
so that they could grow.

00:25:15.470 --> 00:25:19.730 align:middle line:84%
But as you get further and
further into denser realms,

00:25:19.730 --> 00:25:23.690 align:middle line:84%
that force of opposition
can become extreme

00:25:23.690 --> 00:25:25.760 align:middle line:84%
and take on the attributes
of what we call evil.

00:25:25.760 --> 00:25:28.370 align:middle line:84%
So in other words, it
can be so individualistic

00:25:28.370 --> 00:25:31.910 align:middle line:84%
that you think of only
yourself and nobody else.

00:25:31.910 --> 00:25:33.740 align:middle line:90%
And you can hurt other people.

00:25:33.740 --> 00:25:38.780 align:middle line:84%
Psychopaths, Hitlers--
that's the extreme

00:25:38.780 --> 00:25:39.980 align:middle line:90%
that opposition can go to.

00:25:39.980 --> 00:25:42.500 align:middle line:84%
So there are shades
of opposition.

00:25:42.500 --> 00:25:43.920 align:middle line:90%
There are shades of shadow.

00:25:43.920 --> 00:25:46.350 align:middle line:90%
And there are shades of light.

00:25:46.350 --> 00:25:48.120 align:middle line:90%
It's not like an either/or.

00:25:48.120 --> 00:25:51.170 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of
nuances in between.

00:25:51.170 --> 00:25:54.030 align:middle line:84%
But the dimension
that Sophia created

00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:56.850 align:middle line:84%
as a result of her action was
the dimension of soul-mind

00:25:56.850 --> 00:25:58.380 align:middle line:90%
or the dimension of psyche.

00:25:58.380 --> 00:26:01.620 align:middle line:84%
Now, here is where you start
to see light and shadow come

00:26:01.620 --> 00:26:02.460 align:middle line:90%
into play.

00:26:02.460 --> 00:26:07.050 align:middle line:84%
Because you still have the
impulses and the archetypes

00:26:07.050 --> 00:26:09.060 align:middle line:84%
from the spirit realm
that they came from.

00:26:09.060 --> 00:26:10.320 align:middle line:90%
But they were diluted.

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:14.040 align:middle line:84%
They now became shadows so
that in the Gnostic texts,

00:26:14.040 --> 00:26:16.470 align:middle line:84%
and I think even in
the Casey tradition,

00:26:16.470 --> 00:26:18.150 align:middle line:90%
they posited on Earth.

00:26:18.150 --> 00:26:19.740 align:middle line:84%
But it wasn't the
Earth that we know.

00:26:19.740 --> 00:26:21.330 align:middle line:90%
It was like an etheric Earth.

00:26:21.330 --> 00:26:22.860 align:middle line:90%
It was a template of--

00:26:22.860 --> 00:26:24.540 align:middle line:90%
a blueprint of the Earth.

00:26:24.540 --> 00:26:27.990 align:middle line:84%
And that would have come
from the mind of the source.

00:26:27.990 --> 00:26:31.350 align:middle line:84%
Well, when in
Sophia's dimension,

00:26:31.350 --> 00:26:33.115 align:middle line:84%
they started the beings
there because they

00:26:33.115 --> 00:26:34.740 align:middle line:84%
were looking for
individual experience,

00:26:34.740 --> 00:26:36.640 align:middle line:90%
started messing with that.

00:26:36.640 --> 00:26:40.050 align:middle line:84%
And that's where
you start to get

00:26:40.050 --> 00:26:41.460 align:middle line:90%
degrees of light and shadow.

00:26:41.460 --> 00:26:44.700 align:middle line:84%
Because the archetypes would
have been the guiding images.

00:26:44.700 --> 00:26:48.660 align:middle line:84%
But now these souls
were off for themselves.

00:26:48.660 --> 00:26:51.000 align:middle line:84%
And they were developing
their own ways

00:26:51.000 --> 00:26:54.000 align:middle line:84%
to use their creative powers,
misusing their creative powers,

00:26:54.000 --> 00:26:55.740 align:middle line:90%
you could say, in some ways.

00:26:55.740 --> 00:26:59.220 align:middle line:84%
And ultimately, that misuse
of the creative power

00:26:59.220 --> 00:27:03.810 align:middle line:84%
led to the second fall of
soul into material experience,

00:27:03.810 --> 00:27:05.440 align:middle line:90%
into material bodies.

00:27:05.440 --> 00:27:08.700 align:middle line:84%
So you can see that
desire for experience

00:27:08.700 --> 00:27:11.370 align:middle line:84%
was progressing into
all forms, including,

00:27:11.370 --> 00:27:15.430 align:middle line:84%
finally, a spiritual
being in physical form,

00:27:15.430 --> 00:27:17.130 align:middle line:90%
which is what human beings are.

00:27:17.130 --> 00:27:19.950 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So now we're
in more or less one

00:27:19.950 --> 00:27:23.020 align:middle line:84%
of the denser realms of
creation at this point.

00:27:23.020 --> 00:27:29.090 align:middle line:84%
And so the supposition is that
we have to, through experience,

00:27:29.090 --> 00:27:34.240 align:middle line:84%
through opposition, learn
our way back toward more

00:27:34.240 --> 00:27:35.380 align:middle line:90%
of the original template.

00:27:35.380 --> 00:27:39.367 align:middle line:84%
Can you explain in this body of
work what that would look like?

00:27:39.367 --> 00:27:41.200 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Yeah, that's
pretty much accurate,

