the same matrix or function

00:28:45.770 --> 00:28:46.640 align:middle line:90%
of creation.

00:28:46.640 --> 00:28:50.180 align:middle line:84%
So once people understand
that-- and I think

00:28:50.180 --> 00:28:51.710 align:middle line:90%
it's inspirational to people.

00:28:51.710 --> 00:28:54.303 align:middle line:84%
