it as a smooth energy.

00:30:04.050 --> 00:30:07.350 align:middle line:84%
But it gets compartmentalized
at some points.

00:30:07.350 --> 00:30:12.060 align:middle line:84%
And the best way I can
liken it to you is this.

00:30:12.060 --> 00:30:14.340 align:middle line:90%
All right, I live in Florida.

00:30:14.340 --> 00:30:18.270 align:middle line:84%
