waterspouts in Florida.

00:30:18.270 --> 00:30:21.390 align:middle line:84%
Waterspouts are essentially
waterborne tornadoes.

00:30:21.390 --> 00:30:24.083 align:middle line:90%
And they just develop.

00:30:24.083 --> 00:30:25.500 align:middle line:84%
I'm not even sure
why they happen.

00:30:25.500 --> 00:30:27.990 align:middle line:84%
But you can have a
smooth river flowing.

00:30:27.990 --> 00:30:30.180 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden,
you have this disruption

00:30:30.180 --> 00:30:34.410 align:middle line:84%
of this waterspout, which
is a little cyclone.

00:30:34.410 --> 00:30:35.790 align:middle line:90%
You don't want to be near them.

00:30:35.790 --> 00:30:37.620 align:middle line:84%
And they can do
some real damage.

00:30:37.620 --> 00:30:40.535 align:middle line:84%
But you look at that
waterspout, and you

00:30:40.535 --> 00:30:42.660 align:middle line:84%
look at that as something
different from the river,

00:30:42.660 --> 00:30:44.820 align:middle line:84%
the water that it came
from, but it's not.

00:30:44.820 --> 00:30:46.170 align:middle line:90%
The water is smooth.

00:30:46.170 --> 00:30:48.030 align:middle line:90%
But this is a disruption.

00:30:48.030 --> 00:30:49.783 align:middle line:84%
And the disruption
takes on the appearance

00:30:49.783 --> 00:30:50.700 align:middle line:90%
of something separate.

00:30:50.700 --> 00:30:52.080 align:middle line:90%
But it's really not.

00:30:52.080 --> 00:30:56.550 align:middle line:84%
So in this manner,
our reality is

00:30:56.550 --> 00:30:59.560 align:middle line:84%
like a blemish or a blip
in this quantum field.

00:30:59.560 --> 00:31:02.110 align:middle line:84%
It's like a compartment
in this quantum field.

00:31:02.110 --> 00:31:04.240 align:middle line:84%
And within that
compartment, we operate

00:31:04.240 --> 00:31:06.580 align:middle line:84%
under certain laws and
perceptions and beliefs

00:31:06.580 --> 00:31:07.520 align:middle line:90%
and things like that.

00:31:07.520 --> 00:31:09.320 align:middle line:84%
But we're really all
part of that stream--

00:31:09.320 --> 00:31:10.120 align:middle line:90%
that main stream.

00:31:10.120 --> 00:31:12.148 align:middle line:84%
We're just kind of
cul-de-sacked into believing

00:31:12.148 --> 00:31:13.440 align:middle line:90%
that we're something different.

00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:15.610 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So let's talk--
