00:32:08.170 --> 00:32:09.940 align:middle line:84%
The Gnostics called
them archons.

00:32:09.940 --> 00:32:12.040 align:middle line:90%
They were these strange beings.

00:32:12.040 --> 00:32:13.930 align:middle line:84%
And incidentally,
