00:36:55.350 --> 00:36:58.920 align:middle line:84%
Like Egypt before 3000
BC was both a matriarchal

00:36:58.920 --> 00:37:00.540 align:middle line:90%
and a matrilineal society.

00:37:00.540 --> 00:37:03.810 align:middle line:84%
It eventually shifted
and became patriarchal.

00:37:03.810 --> 00:37:05.885 align:middle line:84%
And I have my theories
about why that happened.

00:37:05.885 --> 00:37:10.330 align:middle line:84%
I think when spirit came down
into this world after a while,

00:37:10.330 --> 00:37:13.840 align:middle line:90%
it had to live in danger--

00:37:13.840 --> 00:37:16.150 align:middle line:84%
saber-toothed tigers,
things trying to kill it,

00:37:16.150 --> 00:37:17.623 align:middle line:90%
things happening, bad weather.

00:37:17.623 --> 00:37:19.540 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: When survival
became the imperative.

00:37:19.540 --> 00:37:21.280 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Survival
became imperative.

00:37:21.280 --> 00:37:26.440 align:middle line:84%
And the-- it was really more
of a left brain function

00:37:26.440 --> 00:37:28.840 align:middle line:84%
to deal with that, how
to organize yourself

00:37:28.840 --> 00:37:30.110 align:middle line:90%
against your environment.

00:37:30.110 --> 00:37:32.655 align:middle line:84%
And that's a patriarchal
male way of looking at it.

00:37:32.655 --> 00:37:34.030 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well,
and also the male

00:37:34.030 --> 00:37:36.550 align:middle line:84%
was more equipped to do that
just by size and strength

00:37:36.550 --> 00:37:36.970 align:middle line:90%
alone.

00:37:36.970 --> 00:37:37.770 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:37:37.770 --> 00:37:40.030 align:middle line:90%
So there was a shift.

00:37:40.030 --> 00:37:45.830 align:middle line:84%
But what the feminine always
represented was the really--

00:37:45.830 --> 00:37:50.590 align:middle line:84%
in my opinion, the gateway
back to the spiritual world.

00:37:50.590 --> 00:37:52.200 align:middle line:90%
Because it involves feeling.

00:37:52.200 --> 00:37:53.200 align:middle line:90%
And it involves insight.

00:37:53.200 --> 00:37:54.610 align:middle line:90%
And it involves intuition.

00:37:54.610 --> 00:37:59.110 align:middle line:84%
And if you have those qualities,
you're on a spiritual path.

00:37:59.110 --> 00:38:01.030 align:middle line:84%
You're already connected
to the spirit--

00:38:01.030 --> 00:38:01.840 align:middle line:90%
to spiritual hub.

00:38:01.840 --> 00:38:04.595 align:middle line:84%
Now, that doesn't mean
that only women have that.

00:38:04.595 --> 00:38:05.470 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:38:05.470 --> 00:38:05.710 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Don't mistake that.

00:38:05.710 --> 00:38:07.960 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's feminine,
not necessarily women.

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:10.480 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Jung called it
the anima and the animus,

00:38:10.480 --> 00:38:13.180 align:middle line:84%
the male and the female and
the female and the male.

00:38:13.180 --> 00:38:16.610 align:middle line:84%
And very much like
a saying of Jesus,

00:38:16.610 --> 00:38:18.820 align:middle line:84%
Jesus said when you
make the male female

00:38:18.820 --> 00:38:21.535 align:middle line:84%
and the female male, and
you make the two as one,

00:38:21.535 --> 00:38:23.470 align:middle line:84%
then you will realize
the kingdom of heaven.

00:38:23.470 --> 00:38:24.880 align:middle line:90%
Jung said the exact same thing.

00:38:24.880 --> 00:38:28.450 align:middle line:84%
That when you merge those,
you become an individuated,

00:38:28.450 --> 00:38:30.520 align:middle line:90%
actualized human being.

00:38:30.520 --> 00:38:32.110 align:middle line:84%
That you become
the essence of what

00:38:32.110 --> 00:38:33.430 align:middle line:90%
it means to be a human being.

00:38:33.430 --> 00:38:34.430 align:middle line:90%
You are in balance now.

00:38:34.430 --> 00:38:35.230 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:38:35.230 --> 00:38:38.200 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: And so but the
feminine quality always played

00:38:38.200 --> 00:38:39.580 align:middle line:90%
a very important role in that.

00:38:39.580 --> 00:38:41.320 align:middle line:90%
And I liken it to a rocket ship.

00:38:41.320 --> 00:38:43.960 align:middle line:84%
Because there's two basic
systems in a rocket ship.

00:38:43.960 --> 00:38:45.850 align:middle line:90%
You have the fuel.

00:38:45.850 --> 00:38:47.330 align:middle line:84%
And you have the
guidance system.

00:38:47.330 --> 00:38:51.790 align:middle line:84%
So the fuel is the
feminine aspect of it.

00:38:51.790 --> 00:38:53.848 align:middle line:90%
That is the insight to uplift.

00:38:53.848 --> 00:38:55.390 align:middle line:84%
That there's something
else up there.

00:38:55.390 --> 00:38:57.800 align:middle line:84%
And I want to work
my way towards it.

00:38:57.800 --> 00:39:02.320 align:middle line:84%
But the guidance system is what
helps you shape your direction

00:39:02.320 --> 00:39:03.910 align:middle line:90%
once you've achieved liftoff.

00:39:03.910 --> 00:39:05.760 align:middle line:84%
One is not good
without the other.

00:39:05.760 --> 00:39:07.722 align:middle line:84%
Without the fuel, you
don't get off the ground.

00:39:07.722 --> 00:39:10.180 align:middle line:84%
Without the guidance system,
you just go around in circles.

00:39:10.180 --> 00:39:12.090 align:middle line:84%
So they both play a
very important part.

00:39:12.090 --> 00:39:13.365 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Back to logos
and prima materia.

00:39:13.365 --> 00:39:13.860 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:39:13.860 --> 00:39:16.152 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: They work together
to create whatever reality

00:39:16.152 --> 00:39:17.370 align:middle line:90%
is intended to be created.

00:39:17.370 --> 00:39:18.570 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: They
must work together.

00:39:18.570 --> 00:39:20.612 align:middle line:84%
Because that's the way
the original polarity was.

00:39:20.612 --> 00:39:22.500 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Exactly, and
still is, obviously,

00:39:22.500 --> 00:39:24.285 align:middle line:84%
throughout the universe and
throughout the dimensions.

00:39:24.285 --> 00:39:25.085 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Right.

00:39:25.085 --> 00:39:28.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And so now we get
to the little debate about

00:39:28.170 --> 00:39:31.490 align:middle line:90%
but was this all by design?

00:39:31.490 --> 00:39:34.020 align:middle line:84%
Was it the intention
of the great source

00:39:34.020 --> 00:39:37.560 align:middle line:84%
and the great creator to only
have the thought forms that

00:39:37.560 --> 00:39:40.710 align:middle line:84%
are all essentially
of goodness, or was

00:39:40.710 --> 00:39:44.040 align:middle line:84%
it to expand beyond
that to give universes

00:39:44.040 --> 00:39:46.830 align:middle line:84%
of experienced
birth, which Sophia

00:39:46.830 --> 00:39:48.280 align:middle line:90%
was responsible for doing?

00:39:48.280 --> 00:39:49.080 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Yeah.

00:39:49.080 --> 00:39:53.335 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It seems to me like
she's the one that created this

00:39:53.335 --> 00:39:54.135 align:middle line:90%
entire--

00:39:54.135 --> 00:39:58.530 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: The Gnostics had a
bit of a dual view on that.

00:39:58.530 --> 00:40:02.400 align:middle line:84%
On one hand, they described
her as being imprudent, rash.

00:40:02.400 --> 00:40:05.020 align:middle line:84%
They even described
her as being a whore.

00:40:05.020 --> 00:40:05.820 align:middle line:90%
That she--

00:40:05.820 --> 00:40:07.195 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Find
that in the Bible.

00:40:07.195 --> 00:40:11.097 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: That she
adulterated her high energies

00:40:11.097 --> 00:40:12.180 align:middle line:90%
with these lower elements.

00:40:12.180 --> 00:40:14.380 align:middle line:84%
They didn't mean it
in a carnal sense,

00:40:14.380 --> 00:40:16.210 align:middle line:90%
but in a spiritual sense.

00:40:16.210 --> 00:40:17.220 align:middle line:84%
So that she was a prostitute
in a spiritual sense.

00:40:17.220 --> 00:40:19.053 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So that was
one school of thought.

00:40:19.053 --> 00:40:21.367 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: But another school
of thought was that no,

00:40:21.367 --> 00:40:22.950 align:middle line:84%
this was all known
from the beginning.

00:40:22.950 --> 00:40:26.760 align:middle line:84%
Now, I tend to go with
that latter belief

00:40:26.760 --> 00:40:29.190 align:middle line:84%
because I believe you
have, essentially,

00:40:29.190 --> 00:40:30.510 align:middle line:90%
an all-knowing source.

00:40:30.510 --> 00:40:33.780 align:middle line:84%
And I have to believe
that although I

00:40:33.780 --> 00:40:37.920 align:middle line:84%
do believe that there's degrees
of freedom and latitude allowed

00:40:37.920 --> 00:40:41.010 align:middle line:84%
within that scheme of
things, I do believe

00:40:41.010 --> 00:40:42.840 align:middle line:90%
it's working towards an--

00:40:42.840 --> 00:40:45.075 align:middle line:90%
a guided ending.

00:40:45.075 --> 00:40:47.730 align:middle line:84%
And so in that
regard, yeah, I think

00:40:47.730 --> 00:40:49.445 align:middle line:84%
it was foreseen that
this would happen.

00:40:49.445 --> 00:40:50.710 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I agree with you.

00:40:50.710 --> 00:40:52.650 align:middle line:84%
I think that is how
it was to have been.

00:40:52.650 --> 00:40:54.460 align:middle line:90%
And hence, we're here.

00:40:54.460 --> 00:40:55.260 align:middle line:90%
We're embodied.

00:40:55.260 --> 00:40:56.593 align:middle line:90%
And we're able to talk about it.

00:40:56.593 --> 00:40:58.680 align:middle line:84%
So going back to the
purpose of your work, which

00:40:58.680 --> 00:41:02.010 align:middle line:84%
is, as we spoke
about before, we're

00:41:02.010 --> 00:41:04.290 align:middle line:84%
creating gods every minute
by our own thought--

00:41:04.290 --> 00:41:05.400 align:middle line:90%
collective thought.

00:41:05.400 --> 00:41:10.260 align:middle line:84%
So now to create that critical
mass of that positive noble

00:41:10.260 --> 00:41:13.440 align:middle line:84%
thought again to take
this species of humanity

00:41:13.440 --> 00:41:16.890 align:middle line:84%
back more toward our rightful
place and our rightful state

00:41:16.890 --> 00:41:19.720 align:middle line:84%
of being, what do you think
is most required of each of us

00:41:19.720 --> 00:41:20.520 align:middle line:90%
now?

00:41:20.520 --> 00:41:23.700 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: Well,
obviously, you have

00:41:23.700 --> 00:41:26.970 align:middle line:84%
to have some spiritual
attributes in your life.

00:41:26.970 --> 00:41:30.670 align:middle line:84%
You have to have some vision
of spirit in your life.

00:41:30.670 --> 00:41:32.820 align:middle line:84%
And I think what's required
is you have to work

00:41:32.820 --> 00:41:33.820 align:middle line:90%
towards it a little bit.

00:41:33.820 --> 00:41:35.400 align:middle line:90%
It's like anything else.

00:41:35.400 --> 00:41:37.110 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't just
drop in your lap.

00:41:37.110 --> 00:41:40.260 align:middle line:84%
Now, OK, for some
people, like myself,

00:41:40.260 --> 00:41:44.355 align:middle line:84%
things happen to me
that I didn't seek,

00:41:44.355 --> 00:41:45.990 align:middle line:90%
that just were there.

00:41:45.990 --> 00:41:47.640 align:middle line:90%
OK, that happens to some people.

00:41:47.640 --> 00:41:51.210 align:middle line:84%
Other people, they have to work
more towards that revelation

00:41:51.210 --> 00:41:54.390 align:middle line:84%
or peeling those layers
away for things to happen.

00:41:54.390 --> 00:41:57.270 align:middle line:84%
But we're all capable
of that happening.

00:41:57.270 --> 00:42:01.455 align:middle line:84%
I think the thing to
really understand is this--

00:42:01.455 --> 00:42:06.600 align:middle line:84%
I'm not a big believer in
a lot of New Age adages.

00:42:06.600 --> 00:42:09.180 align:middle line:84%
But the whole thing
about being co-creators

00:42:09.180 --> 00:42:12.450 align:middle line:84%
is really true from
a quantum standpoint,

00:42:12.450 --> 00:42:14.850 align:middle line:84%
as well as from a
spiritual standpoint.

00:42:14.850 --> 00:42:16.770 align:middle line:84%
I likened it to, like
I said, the source--

00:42:16.770 --> 00:42:19.710 align:middle line:84%
let's say the source is the
raw power of a power grid

00:42:19.710 --> 00:42:21.960 align:middle line:84%
like we have power grids
that run this country.

00:42:21.960 --> 00:42:23.430 align:middle line:90%
The source is the raw power.

00:42:23.430 --> 00:42:25.740 align:middle line:84%
Well, raw power is never
transmitted for use.

00:42:25.740 --> 00:42:27.480 align:middle line:90%
It has to be stepped down.

00:42:27.480 --> 00:42:31.500 align:middle line:84%
So it's stepped down into
the-- into relay stations.

00:42:31.500 --> 00:42:33.490 align:middle line:84%
And we're the relay
stations in effect.

00:42:33.490 --> 00:42:35.605 align:middle line:84%
So we are part of
that energy, even

00:42:35.605 --> 00:42:37.980 align:middle line:84%
though in a limited and stepped
down sense-- stepped down

00:42:37.980 --> 00:42:38.780 align:middle line:90%
frequency.

00:42:38.780 --> 00:42:40.440 align:middle line:84%
But we can increase
our frequencies.

00:42:40.440 --> 00:42:42.390 align:middle line:84%
We can increase our
rate of vibration

00:42:42.390 --> 00:42:45.900 align:middle line:84%
by the level of understanding
and experience we have.

00:42:45.900 --> 00:42:48.690 align:middle line:84%
And it's not just enough
to have understanding.

00:42:48.690 --> 00:42:53.010 align:middle line:84%
Because there is a
difference between knowledge

00:42:53.010 --> 00:42:55.450 align:middle line:84%
gained by books and knowledge
gained by experience.

00:42:55.450 --> 00:42:57.450 align:middle line:84%
Knowledge gain by experience
is the higher form.

00:42:57.450 --> 00:43:00.180 align:middle line:84%
Because I could tell you, for
instance, that fire burns.

00:43:00.180 --> 00:43:01.983 align:middle line:84%
But you don't know
that for sure until you

00:43:01.983 --> 00:43:03.150 align:middle line:90%
stick your hand in the fire.

00:43:03.150 --> 00:43:03.960 align:middle line:90%
Then you own it.

00:43:03.960 --> 00:43:05.760 align:middle line:90%
You know what fire's about.

00:43:05.760 --> 00:43:07.850 align:middle line:90%
That's knowledge by experience.

00:43:07.850 --> 00:43:11.960 align:middle line:84%
So the point that I'm trying
to tell people is-- in fact,

00:43:11.960 --> 00:43:15.578 align:middle line:84%
I often start off my public
speaking by saying to people,

00:43:15.578 --> 00:43:17.620 align:middle line:84%
don't believe a damn thing
I'm going to tell you.

00:43:17.620 --> 00:43:19.300 align:middle line:84%
And they sit there scratching
their heads saying, well, what

00:43:19.300 --> 00:43:20.550 align:middle line:90%
do we pay to come to this for?

00:43:20.550 --> 00:43:23.360 align:middle line:84%
I'm saying I'm not telling you
not to pay attention to me.

00:43:23.360 --> 00:43:26.198 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not telling you not
to take in and internalize

00:43:26.198 --> 00:43:27.490 align:middle line:90%
the information I'm giving you.

00:43:27.490 --> 00:43:30.040 align:middle line:84%
What I'm saying is you
don't have to believe me.

00:43:30.040 --> 00:43:32.290 align:middle line:84%
What you have to do
is get to the point

00:43:32.290 --> 00:43:36.220 align:middle line:84%
where you have your own
experiences and revelations

00:43:36.220 --> 00:43:38.090 align:middle line:84%
with this source
that's out there.

00:43:38.090 --> 00:43:39.850 align:middle line:84%
And then you become
your own prophet.

00:43:39.850 --> 00:43:42.430 align:middle line:84%
You don't need somebody
like me to listen to.

00:43:42.430 --> 00:43:44.980 align:middle line:84%
You don't need to look up
to me or any other teacher

00:43:44.980 --> 00:43:46.150 align:middle line:90%
or guru or anything else.

00:43:46.150 --> 00:43:48.850 align:middle line:10%
You can own this
in your own self.

00:43:48.850 --> 00:43:52.930 align:middle line:10%
And all I'm doing is trying to
give the people a roadmap to,

00:43:52.930 --> 00:43:55.705 align:middle line:10%
maybe, maximize
the ability to have

00:43:55.705 --> 00:43:56.830 align:middle line:10%
those kinds of experiences.

00:43:56.830 --> 00:43:58.345 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: To go into
connection with source.

00:43:58.345 --> 00:44:00.820 align:middle line:84%
To go into connection with
your own soul and/or mind.

00:44:00.820 --> 00:44:03.790 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: What I found
is source is like a radio

00:44:03.790 --> 00:44:05.710 align:middle line:90%
station broadcasting 24/7.

00:44:05.710 --> 00:44:09.130 align:middle line:84%
And until I had certain
revelations or awakenings,

00:44:09.130 --> 00:44:11.492 align:middle line:84%
I was like somebody
trying to tune that radio.

00:44:11.492 --> 00:44:12.700 align:middle line:90%
All I was getting was static.

00:44:12.700 --> 00:44:15.280 align:middle line:84%
But then I finally hit
on that one frequency.

00:44:15.280 --> 00:44:18.160 align:middle line:10%
And it became clear to me
that it was like a 24/7

00:44:18.160 --> 00:44:19.330 align:middle line:10%
broadcast of information.

00:44:19.330 --> 00:44:22.090 align:middle line:10%
And it was information that
could really enhance one's life

00:44:22.090 --> 00:44:26.020 align:middle line:10%
and help you really get a
grasp on what reality was about

00:44:26.020 --> 00:44:29.440 align:middle line:10%
and realize that this is
just the bottom ladder

00:44:29.440 --> 00:44:33.490 align:middle line:10%
of multiple dimensions
that are above us

00:44:33.490 --> 00:44:36.970 align:middle line:10%
and that we can get information
from those dimensions

00:44:36.970 --> 00:44:39.800 align:middle line:10%
that we can come and
bring back and use here,

00:44:39.800 --> 00:44:41.218 align:middle line:10%
which was the
basis of shamanism.

00:44:41.218 --> 00:44:42.760 align:middle line:84%
Shamans were those
people that walked

00:44:42.760 --> 00:44:45.400 align:middle line:84%
on the other side, brought
back information for healing,

00:44:45.400 --> 00:44:47.600 align:middle line:84%
for guiding their tribes,
and so forth and so on.

00:44:47.600 --> 00:44:48.400 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Agreed.

00:44:48.400 --> 00:44:49.870 align:middle line:84%
It's a time to be
our own shaman.

00:44:49.870 --> 00:44:52.370 align:middle line:84%
We can go to the higher mind,
which is connected to the all.

00:44:52.370 --> 00:44:53.170 align:middle line:90%
>>CANOVA: Exactly.

00:44:53.170 --> 00:44:55.300 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And so just
finding that, like you say,

00:44:55.300 --> 00:44:57.190 align:middle line:84%
hitting on that
frequency so that you

00:44:57.190 --> 00:44:59.800 align:middle line:84%
can hear that voice
because it's so clear, so

00:44:59.800 --> 00:45:02.740 align:middle line:84%
clean, and, usually,
quite logical too.

00:45:02.740 --> 00:45:04.750 align:middle line:84%
And it's not laden
with all the emotions

00:45:04.750 --> 00:45:06.280 align:middle line:90%
that we have in this realm.

00:45:06.280 --> 00:45:08.050 align:middle line:84%
Might it be fair
also to say in terms

00:45:08.050 --> 00:45:11.140 align:middle line:84%
of the collective of the human
soup that we're creating,

00:45:11.140 --> 00:45:16.600 align:middle line:84%
just to let go of cynicism in
favor of actual discernment?

00:45:16.600 --> 00:45:20.930 align:middle line:84%
Cynicism is really born out
of fear of others' projections

00:45:20.930 --> 00:45:21.730 align:middle line:90%
on us.

00:45:21.730 --> 00:45:23.480 align:middle line:84%
To let go of cynicism
and maybe start

00:45:23.480 --> 00:45:25.480 align:middle line:84%
seeing the good in each
other a little bit more,

00:45:25.480 --> 00:45:28.300 align:middle line:84%
might that help the
soup start, essentially,

00:45:28.300 --> 00:45:30.310 align:middle line:90%
simmering a bit faster--

00:45:30.310 --> 00:45:31.172 align:middle line:90%
simmer a bit faster?

00:45:31.172 --> 00:45:33.130 align:middle line:84%
>>CANOVA: I think fear
is probably the greatest

